myfiles=list()
proffile=list()


 tempname=str_split(temp,pattern = ".csv") %>% unlist() %>% 
   as.data.frame(StringAsFactor=FALSE)


for (i in c(1:length(temp))) {
  data=read_csv(temp[i])
  myfiles[[i]]=data %>% 
    mutate(Symbol=tempname$.[i*2-1],prof1year=data$Close[255]-data$Open[1],prof2year=data$Close[505]-data$Open[1],
           prof5year=data$Close[1261]-data$Open[1]) 

   dataprof=myfiles[[i]] %>% select(Symbol,prof1year,prof2year,prof5year)
   proffile[[i]]=dataprof[1,]
  
}
companyprof=do.call("rbind",proffile)
companyprof=merge(companyprof,constituents)

top1year=companyprof %>% group_by(Sector) %>% mutate(rank=rank(-prof1year)) %>% 
  arrange(Sector,rank) %>% filter(rank<11) %>% select(Symbol,prof1year,Sector,rank)

rank1year=companyprof %>% group_by(Sector) %>% mutate(rank=rank(-prof1year)) %>% 
  arrange(Sector,rank) %>% filter(rank==1)%>% select(Symbol,Sector)

top2year=companyprof %>% group_by(Sector) %>% mutate(rank=rank(-prof2year)) %>% 
  arrange(Sector,rank) %>% filter(rank<11) %>% select(Symbol,prof2year,Sector,rank)

rank2year=companyprof %>% group_by(Sector) %>% mutate(rank=rank(-prof1year)) %>% 
  arrange(Sector,rank) %>% filter(rank==1)%>% select(Symbol,Sector)

top5year=companyprof %>% group_by(Sector) %>% mutate(rank=rank(-prof5year)) %>% 
  arrange(Sector,rank) %>% filter(rank<11) %>% select(Symbol,prof5year,Sector,rank)

rank5year=companyprof %>% group_by(Sector) %>% mutate(rank=rank(-prof1year)) %>% 
  arrange(Sector,rank) %>% filter(rank==1) %>% select(Symbol,Sector)

top1year %>% hchart("column",hcaes(x=Sector,y=prof1year,group=Symbol))
top2year %>% hchart("column",hcaes(x=Sector,y=prof2year,group=Symbol))

meandate13=data.frame(prof=seq(0,0,length.out = length(temp)))
meannotdate13=data.frame(prof=seq(0,0,length.out = length(temp)))

for (i in c(1:length(temp))) {
  
  date13=myfiles[[i]] %>% mutate(date13=str_detect(Date,pattern = "-13"),dayprof=Close-Open) %>% 
   filter(date13==TRUE) %>% select(dayprof) 
  notdate13=myfiles[[i]] %>% mutate(date13=str_detect(Date,pattern = "-13"),dayprof=Close-Open) %>% 
    filter(date13==FALSE) %>% select(dayprof)
  meandate13$prof[i]=mean(date13$dayprof,na.rm = TRUE)
  meannotdate13$prof[i]=mean(notdate13$dayprof,na.rm = TRUE)
}

t.test(meandate13,meannotdate13)

#plot size vs component
imagesize=matrix(0,nrow = 40,ncol = 1)

for (component in seq(10,400,length.out = 40)) {
feature.vector = pca.img$rotation[,1:component]
compact.data = t(feature.vector) %*% t(img)
approx.img = t(feature.vector %*% compact.data) 
#saving
library(imager)
#Create temporary file
tmpF <- tempfile(fileext=".png")
myimage=as.cimg(approx.img)
save.image(myimage,tmpF)
imagesize[component/10]=file.info(tmpF)$size
}
